 게 아닙니다&amp;quot;&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5b7b1;strokeColor=#e74c3c;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=8;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="140" y="120" width="260" height="120" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="s1_2" value="&lt;b&gt;1-2. 충격 통계 (5분)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px;&quot;&gt;850만 일자리 대체&lt;br&gt;43% AI 사용 / 56% 교육 0&lt;br&gt;연 500시간 = 62.5일 손실&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5b7b1;strokeColor=#e74c3c;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=8;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="415" y="120" width="260" height="120" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="s1_2b" value="&lt;b&gt;1-2b. 나의 현실 (3분)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px;&quot;&gt;[실제 캘린더 데이터]&lt;br&gt;6주 120건 미팅 / 382.8시간&lt;br&gt;주당 20건 / 63.8시간&lt;br&gt;&amp;quot;미팅만으로 주 63시간&amp;quot;&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5b7b1;strokeColor=#e74c3c;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=8;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="690" y="120" width="260" height="120" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="s1_3" value="&lt;b&gt;1-3. 마지막 기회 (4분)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px;&quot;&gt;AI 타임라인 2022-2027&lt;br&gt;엑셀 거부 회계사 = 실직&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5b7b1;strokeColor=#e74c3c;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=8;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="965" y="120" width="260" height="120" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="s1_4" value="&lt;b&gt;1-4. 역설 선언 (3분)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;주식 강의가 중요한 게 아니다&amp;quot;&lt;br&gt;이중 트랙: 투자 + AI&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5b7b1;strokeColor=#e74c3c;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=8;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="1240" y="120" width="260" height="120" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="q_s1" value="&lt;i&gt;&amp;quot;아는 것만으로는 충분하지 않다. 적용해야 한다&amp;quot; — Goethe&lt;/i&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=9;fontStyle=2;fontColor=#888888;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="400" y="255" width="400" height="20" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="tr_s1s2" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px; color:#c0392b;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;깨어 있으면 뭐가 달라지는지 보여드리겠습니다...&amp;quot;&lt;/font&gt;" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;html=1;strokeColor=#c0392b;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=10;entryX=0.5;entryY=0;entryDx=0;entryDy=0;exitX=0.5;exitY=1;exitDx=0;exitDy=0;" parent="1" source="s1box" target="s2box" edge="1"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="s2box" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:16px; color:#ffffff;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;SECTION 2 : &amp;quot;나는 이렇게 빡세게 산다&amp;quot; — 개인 스토리 (28분) : 경외/공감&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#1a6496;strokeColor=#154360;fontColor=#ffffff;fontSize=16;verticalAlign=top;arcSize=4;spacingTop=8;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="120" y="340" width="1500" height="650" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="s2_1_header" value="&lt;b&gt;2-1. 12가지 역할 공개 (7분)&lt;/b&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=12;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontStyle=1;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="140" y="370" width="250" height="20" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="s2_1_box" value="" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#aed6f1;strokeColor=#5dade2;arcSize=4;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="140" y="395" width="1460" height="180" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="r1" value="&lt;b&gt;1. 교보그룹&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;디플래닉스 조직장&lt;br&gt;(임원)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d6eaf8;strokeColor=#85c1e9;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=9;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=10;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="155" y="405" width="220" height="70" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="r2" value="&lt;b&gt;2. 데이터 사업&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;기획자&lt;br&gt;KANDLE/AI Studio" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d6eaf8;strokeColor=#85c1e9;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=9;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=10;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="390" y="405" width="220" height="70" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="r3" value="&lt;b&gt;3. AI 컨설턴트&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;금융사 생성형AI&lt;br&gt;도입 자문" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d6eaf8;strokeColor=#85c1e9;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=9;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=10;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="625" y="405" width="220" height="70" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="r4" value="&lt;b&gt;4. 만화카페 사장&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;150평&lt;br&gt;book.frindle.synology.me" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d6eaf8;strokeColor=#85c1e9;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=9;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=10;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="860" y="405" width="220" height="70" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="r5" value="&lt;b&gt;5. 주식 강사&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;유튜브 112편&lt;br&gt;지금 이 순간" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d6eaf8;strokeColor=#85c1e9;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=9;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=10;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="1095" y="405" width="220" height="70" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="r6" value="&lt;b&gt;6. 엑셀 강사&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;광화문&lt;br&gt;생산성본부" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d6eaf8;strokeColor=#85c1e9;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=9;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=10;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="1330" y="405" width="220" height="70" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="r7" value="&lt;b&gt;7. 쌍둥이 아빠&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;8살&lt;br&gt;결혼 늦게" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d6eaf8;strokeColor=#85c1e9;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=9;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=10;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="155" y="490" width="220" height="70" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="r8" value="&lt;b&gt;8. 이직 준비생&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;이 와중에&lt;br&gt;병행 중" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d6eaf8;strokeColor=#85c1e9;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=9;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=10;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="390" y="490" width="220" height="70" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="r9" value="&lt;b&gt;9. 경매 투자자&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;부동산 경매&lt;br&gt;경험자" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d6eaf8;strokeColor=#85c1e9;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=9;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=10;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="625" y="490" width="220" height="70" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="r10" value="&lt;b&gt;10. 해외구매대행&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;새 수익원&lt;br&gt;탐색 중" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d6eaf8;strokeColor=#85c1e9;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=9;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=10;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="860" y="490" width="220" height="70" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="r11" value="&lt;b&gt;11. 자판기 사업&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;국가유공자&lt;br&gt;생업지원" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d6eaf8;strokeColor=#85c1e9;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=9;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=10;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="1095" y="490" width="220" height="70" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="r12" value="&lt;b&gt;12. 퀀트 개발자&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;US Stock&lt;br&gt;AI 시스템" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d6eaf8;strokeColor=#85c1e9;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=9;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=10;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="1330" y="490" width="220" height="70" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="s2_2" value="&lt;b&gt;2-2. 비밀 공개 (5분)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px;&quot;&gt;Claude Code $200 x 4계정&lt;br&gt;= $800/월&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;멀티계정 아키텍처:&lt;br&gt;claude-a / b / c / cloud&lt;br&gt;17개 MCP 동시 연결&lt;br&gt;4개가 동시에 다른 일&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;비용최적화 3설정&lt;br&gt;$800→$400/월(50%↓)&lt;br&gt;23스킬+106자동화&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#85c1e9;strokeColor=#5dade2;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=8;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="140" y="590" width="320" height="190" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="s2_2b" value="&lt;b&gt;2-2b. YouTube→LLM Wiki (3분)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px;&quot;&gt;Telegram→자막추출→요약&lt;br&gt;→주제별 Obsidian 저장&lt;br&gt;→LLM Wiki 자동 반영&lt;br&gt;22KB가 3,551파일 대체&lt;br&gt;&amp;quot;AI의 두뇌 노트&amp;quot;&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#85c1e9;strokeColor=#5dade2;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=8;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="475" y="590" width="320" height="190" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="s2_2c" value="&lt;b&gt;2-2c. Synology NAS (2분)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px;&quot;&gt;book.frindle.synology.me&lt;br&gt;코드수정→5분 자동배포&lt;br&gt;Jenkins CI/CD 6단계&lt;br&gt;9번 빌드 성공&lt;br&gt;&amp;quot;집 컴퓨터가 홈페이지 관리&amp;quot;&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#85c1e9;strokeColor=#5dade2;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=middle;arcSize=8;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="810" y="590" width="320" height="190" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="s2_3_header" value="&lt;b&gt;2-3. 충격 데모 7연발 (8분)&lt;/b&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=12;fontColor=#1a1a2e;fontStyle=1;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="140" y="790" width="250" height="20" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="s2_3_box" value="" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#85c1e9;strokeColor=#5dade2;arcSize=6;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="140" y="810" width="1460" height="80" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="d1" value="&lt;b&gt;D1: PLAUD&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;주 20건 회의록&lt;br&gt;자동 5분" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wra